Text: The event log shows a business process likely for application processing Activities are Examining Event Log The event log details a business process likely related to application processing Key activities include Receive Application RA Validate Form VF Assess Eligibility AE and Request Missing Info RMI Another activity AD appears but is incomplete suggesting potential additional steps in the process

Text: The process includes Approval Decision AD after eligibility assessment followed by Send Confirmation SC and Archive Case AC Specific cases show variations Case 1 and Case 3 involve Request Missing Info RMI loops before AD while Case 2 proceeds directly to AD
